Overview:
The mixture of cold Atlantic water and coarse sand in your mouth brings you back from unconsciousness. Surrounded by the wreckage of a boatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s hull, you can only draw one conclusion: your vessel has been torn apart by the submerged rocks. The secrets of the island must be uncovered if you are ever going to find a way to escape. Where is everyone; is the island really uninhabited; and what is lurking within the isolated caves?

A disturbing psychological thriller set in the bleakness of an abandoned island, combining exploration and in depth puzzle solving.

Montague's Mount is an exploration game with a story that leaves questions unanswered and open to interpretation. The developers have announced that they will return to Montague's Mount in one art form or another. 
